  Locus:
    Page: 355
    Verse: 9
Tags:
  - Peace/Harmony
---
A happy person is not his own enemy, does not carry on an endless war with
his soul. We may be fiercely at odds with the wrongs of the world around
us. But inside ourselves, near the core, if we are happy, we are at peace.
